    <p style="text-align: justify;">
      <strong>Speak another language?</strong>  Heyu is the easiest way to add dual-langauge subtitles to any YouTube video. Share content you love. Keep your language skills fresh.</p> <br>
    <h2>Explore.</h2>
      <p> Love <strong>Bollywood videos</strong> or <strong>bossa nova songs</strong>, but have no idea what the lyrics mean?  Heyu helps you explore new worlds by adding meaning to music and video in other langauges.</p> <br>
    <h2>Learn.</h2>
      <p>Practice pronounciation, grammar, vocabulary through music.</p> <br>
